questions.NNQT_istance: Which are the settlement that contains more than 100 architectural structure
questions.correct_NNQT_istance: Which are the settlement that contains more than 100 architectural structures
questions.query:
SELECT ?uri COUNT(?obj)
	WHERE {  ?obj a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/ArchitecturalStructure>. ?uri a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Settlement>. ?obj <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/location> ?uri.} GROUP BY ?uri HAVING(COUNT(?obj)>100)
